"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"A reader asked me if I had ever written about the infrastructure I use to run AVC. We both searched the archives and could not find a post on that topic.\\n\\nSo here it is:\\n\\n1/ Content Management System – [WordPress](https://wordpress.org/) – I use the open source software version of WordPress to write these posts and manage them.\\n\\n2/ Hosting Provider – [Cloudways](https://www.cloudways.com/en/) – I have used a number of hosting providers over the years. If you use WordPress, it is fairly easy to migrate from one to another. Cloudways is the current favorite.\\n\\n3/ Comments – [Twitter Comments Plugin](https://wordpress.org/plugins/discuss-on-twitter/) – I have used various comment systems over the years. I am currently using a WordPress plugin to host the comments on Twitter.\\n\\n4/ Email – [Feedblitz](https://www.feedblitz.com/) – This allows me to send an email out to over 30,000 people whenever I post.\\n\\n5/ Search – [Algolia](https://www.algolia.com/) – Fast and simple to site search.\\n\\nIt’s relatively easy to set all of this up and then you are not locked into a service provider. I strongly recommend this approach.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1624881261,\"title\":\"AVC Infrastructure\",\"publication\":\"avc\"},\"digest\":\"oC4SQJrYhbm2dbBZCGFJh0lTSGlQT1smPtipqMimMaw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB8332710AB60A1B2e8FE6D775d83524C9E0cE136\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FiD2ALymcePeEtTW-G9rQSmcPd1h4mDPeNiqNj5OjGw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"or7Oz7LuQf0j9f0zl2APv4Ys6kh8mj7L66G41AeIimw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"nJu1kJOCa7wqAVvI1qnj_PskTBtBom1lQeYcITTAAqK6IOLhXCaHReEKt9pNEiFbxOCaUjje2d7ebazU8WUuqg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x96db97d26aedf1dd5f41663f7ffb57a210fee4523d6bc3ef803806b7d868f6a83df05cbb0d00049a940e4fbde20b52aa0577568fd8c268b20a7371e071d217811c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on avc.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"FiD2ALymcePeEtTW-G9rQSmcPd1h4mDPeNiqNj5OjGw\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"or7Oz7LuQf0j9f0zl2APv4Ys6kh8mj7L66G41AeIimw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"oC4SQJrYhbm2dbBZCGFJh0lTSGlQT1smPtipqMimMaw\"}"